Package: tnseq
Type: Package
Title: Tn-seq processing and analysis
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-05-10
Author: Paul Jensen
Maintainer: Paul Jensen <paul.jensen@bc.edu>
Description: A complete pipeline for processing and analyzing Tn-seq experiments.
  Functions include read trimming, mapping (via bowtie), normalization, and 
  visualization.  Allows parallel processing and aggregation of samples from 
  multiple conditions, strains, and mutant libraries.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports: 
  dplyr,
  GenomicRanges,
  ggplot2,
  parallel,
  Rcpp (>= 0.11.5),
  stringr,
  tidyr,
  ShortRead
Depends:
  magrittr
Suggests:
  GENE.E
LinkingTo: Rcpp
